<HEADLINE> Woman Dies of Heart Attack During Pope Mass </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SARAJEVO, April 14 (Xinhua) -- An old lady had a heart attack
during Sunday's mass here given by Pope John Paul II and died
later in a hospital, a local newspaper reported.
</P>
<P>
According to Sarajevo daily Dnevni Avaz, Zorana Delic, 56, of
Sarajevo collapsed during the mass at the Kosevo stadium which
were attended by more than 75,000 people.
</P>
<P>
