Congress (NPC) gave an account of issues related to the
implementation of China's Nationality Law in Hong Kong last May,
and afterwards, the preparatory Committee of the HKSAR of the NPC
put forward specific suggestions on the implementation of Article
24 of the Basic Law, which deals with Hong Kong residents' right
of abode.
</P>
<P>
