<HEADLINE> New HSBC Unit to Focus on Trans-Pacific Corporate Finance </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, April 14 (Xinhua) -- Three member corporations of
the HongKong-Shanghai Banking Corporation (HSBC) Group have formed
 a new business to focus on trans-Pacific mergers, acquisitions
and corporate finance activities, it was announced here today.
</P>
