<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, April 14 (Xinhua) -- Thirty Algerian civilians were
massacred by an armed Islamic group on Sunday night in the village
of Douar Shaib Mohammed near Boufarik, 35 kilometers south of the
Algerian capital Algiers.
</P>
<P>
