Boufarik has been repeatedly hit by terrorist attacks over the
past few days, where at least 26 other civilians, including women,
children and an 80-year-old, were killed by massacres and bombing
attacks.
</P>
<P>
The new massacre brought the number of people killed under the
same condition to at least 173 over the past two weeks. 
