<TEXT>
<P>
MEXICO CITY, April 13 (Xinhua) -- Carlos Hermosillo scored a
hat-trick feat to pace Mexico for a 6-0 commanding win over
Jamaica on Sunday in the regional qualifying group for the 1998
World Cup Finals.
</P>
<P>
