qualifying group with seven points, followed by Costa Rica (1-0-1)
and the United States (1-1-1) with four points apiece.
</P>
<P>
Only the top three teams in the six-team division representing
North and Central America and the Caribbean advance to France. El
Salvador, Jamaica and Canada have one point apiece.
</P>
