men and one 80-year-old, were massacred Friday night in Douar
Menaa, also in the region of Boufarik, which is only 30 kilometers
from Algiers.
</P>
<P>
Algerian army and the self-defense militias, backed by military
helicopters, launched a man-hunt on Saturday looking for the
Islamic militants who had committed the killings. 
